-poem-
  who:
   some teacher MS LOW???
  what:
   them
  why:
    idk man (maybe cos they r ur fav tcher)
  when: 
    in exam period 
  how: 
    they helped you 
    1) to find a revision buddy in class to clarify doubts with during lessons and during the weekends 
    2) in providing opportunities for consultation during weekends (if revision buddy can't answer your questions) without complaint 
    3) in finding extra revision materials for you at your request 
    4) by patiently staying back after lessons to explain questions even when it took up their lunch break 
    5) in offering wise advice when you felt uncertain and disappointed, and wanted to give up 
